                                    option(value='', selected, disabled) Select experience level...
                                    option(value='Never coded') Never coded
                                    option(value='Scratch experience') Scratch experience
                                    option(value='Text-based coding') Text-based coding (Python, JavaScript, etc.)
                                    option(value='Advanced programmer') Advanced programmer
                                label(for='codingLevel') Current Coding Experience *
                            
                            // Learning Goal
                            .form-floating.mb-3
